{"chunk": "perdita di pacchetti.\n2.3.4 Servizio circuito virtuale\nNel servizio circuito virtuale due apparecchiature terminali si scambiano dati solo dopo avere \ninstaurato una connessione virtuale che mette in relazione l\u2019una all\u2019altra. Questo servizio si \narticola in tre fasi, analogamente al servizio reso da una rete a commutazione di circuito che \nmette a disposizione una connessione fisica con risorse di comunicazione dedicate, e cio e\u0300 \n \u2013fase di instaurazione, \n \u2013fase dati,\n \u2013fase di rilascio.", "embedding": [0.018663611, 0.041993957, -0.013923764, -0.009704319, -0.0010669162, -0.007853595, 0.06124136, 0.03946804, 0.012704316, -0.020810952, 0.019149628, 0.011285318, 0.048263654, 0.01968925, 0.06365868, -0.08079102, 0.049393937, 0.019409556, -0.06360434, 0.049744677, 0.024885409, 0.017282132, -0.00045918731, -0.024325134, -0.03379136, -0.01974107, 0.036170404, -0.01575895, -0.005875747, -0.0020650495, 0.03961244, 0.003496926, -0.0441045, 0.012912677, -0.025313696, 0.017254913, 0.054450918, 0.00923659, -0.007353008, -0.05465112, 0.01799077, 0.01180568, -0.009557465, 0.032571703, -0.0077915564, -3.0483547e-05, 0.07016477, 0.074338414, -0.04980024, 0.01817534, 0.0032492478, -0.03950446, -0.019106459, 0.04285726, -0.031867787, 0.010875858, -0.0059030685, -0.029370757, 0.03459558, -0.03845096, -0.07418607, 0.044834394, -0.007920017, -0.032931898, 0.021096997, 0.008256111, 0.0013169732, 0.001064579, -0.06814851, -0.007878395, -0.021910125, 0.02991641, -0.08971835, -0.029445961, 0.044662993, -0.050735887, 0.010744682, -0.037274055, -0.0011865468, 0.05202039, -0.006319981, 0.011310798, 0.059046358, 0.0037561045, 0.009988306, -0.014999998, 0.006805231, -0.07666403, -0.03985689, -0.01718766, 0.06038665, 0.006694701, -0.015569125, -0.0052674357, 0.084621914, -0.04101207, -0.08876547, -0.021811955, 0.06275152, 0.054596484, 0.029054753, -0.008839074, 0.019427678, -0.052363805, 0.039238855, 6.2368736e-06, -0.008053189, -0.07353391, -0.0